channel.title: 317 Delta Connection Problems Help Please :/ ASAP
channel.description:
Hi guys i have a problem with getting my rsps online i did all the portfowarding and the no-ip shit and i put in my no-ip address in the GUI.java I changed all the addresses to My no-ip adress I think it might be the port that my source is running can someone please tell me how i can find where this port number is though.
Your help will be very appreciated
Thanks~~~

item.title: 317 Delta Connection Problems Help Please :/ ASAP
item.dc:creator: @cloudslife cloudslife
item.description:
@cloudslife wrote:

  1. Open server File source
  2. find server.txt There will be 2 files the port one is the one with 3 lines with looks like

ClientRequired=0 WorldId=3 ServerPort=43595
3. open the other server file and look for this

and there u go.
need anymore help just PM me
